basically as far as i can tell the review system is dogshit, the "bad" people that shouldn't be boosting your incentive is to not review them fairly just blacklist them or you will get a troll review back the appeal system idk i guess it community driven so a majority don't care i have put in 2 appeals i had troll review back 6/10 provided logs of the 3 keys i did and it got declined the avg person that can read warcraft logs can clearly see my route my dps & kicks was fine the other appeal i put in was when the review system was first implemented you could rate people 0/10 without any comment and even if you finished all the runs i did 5x16 got reviewed 0/10 for a cleared run's with 0 comments and that got declined too 

so tldr is don't worry about it. the lvl10 posters that accept you into keys probably don't even care about your reviews just keep your IO pushed as far as you can go XD

Posters DO care about review system, but only if your review is super low (lower than 7-8/10)
You simply **cannot** get lower than 6/10 on successful keys
The review system is NOT a measure for how skillful you are. It's a review about YOU. Meaning your personality and your likebility
If you be intimidating or rude, the system is intended to let other players review you low
